Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.04,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1\move(300,1065,45,1065)}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:09.17,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}哼哼喘着粗气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.26,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}沿着走廊一阵风跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:17.38,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,150)}今晚是你最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:20.43,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}你想吃的就是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.43,0:01:21.51,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\blur3\fad(0,0)\i1}就是这个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:25.60,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}加上你就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:30.02,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,300)}美食和大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:34.03,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我是个围裙男孩
