Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:46.75,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,0)}围裙男孩 你的笑容是绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.12,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}我们家团团圆圆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.42,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,0)}笑声满满
