Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些要放在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,书都放在那边房间的角落里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚底注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果绊到摔碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是些贵重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个就那样放着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心打开很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 放在我房间的桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远坂的房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我进去这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 士郎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我顺便看看樱怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算让我送去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远坂的房间在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远坂家真够大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐那边搞完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 她让我帮忙把这个搬去桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就放在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樱 这边怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有进展
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但还有很多要做的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我整理了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都扔在桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英国 伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是时钟塔来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有好几年都是这样交流的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来就够忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远坂很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去姐姐那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正想去叫你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午饭要吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借厨房一下 我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你们来帮忙的 还要你做饭怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,围裙用那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猫图案…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐喜欢猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,材料应该凑齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋 胡萝卜 大葱 青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鱼糕 叉烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好咧 都齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天吃炒饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得姐姐应该会做中华
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中华平时都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是姐姐能教我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是什么能教人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能马上帮我切菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叉烧 胡萝卜 鱼糕 大葱 青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切饭粒大小的丁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了快速均匀过火 以及口感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本想看看有什么要帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还是不要打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就静静等着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
